quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,87,"un logon ne ghar bethnay valyon mein shaamil hona pasand kya aur un ke dilon par thp_h laga diya gaya, is liye un ki samajh mein ab kuch nahi aata"
9,88,bakhilaf is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne aur un logon ne jo Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath imaan laaye thay a panni jaan o maal se jehaad kya aur ab saari bhalaiyan unhi ke liye hain aur wohi Falah panay walay hain
9,89,"Allah ne un ke liye aisay baagh tayyar rakhay hain jin ke neechay nhrin bah rahi hain, un mein woh hamesha rahen ge yeh hai azeem al shan kamyabi"
9,90,badwi arbo mein se bhi bohat se log aeye jinhon ne izr kiye taakay inhen bhi peechay reh jaane ki ijazat di jaye iss terhan baith rahay woh log jinhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool se imaan ka jhoota ehad kya tha unbadwiyoonmein se jin logon ne kufar ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya hai anqareeb woh dard naak saza se dochar hon ge
9,91,"zaeef aur bemaar log aur woh log jo shirkat jehaad ke liye raah nahi paate, agar peechay reh jayen to koi harj nahi jabkay woh khuloos dil ke sath Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke wafadar hon aisay mohsineenpar aitraaz ki koi gunjaish nahi hai aur Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
9,92,"isi terhan unn logon par bhi koi aitraaz ka mauqa nahi hai jinhon ne khud aa kar tum se darkhwast ki thi ke hamaray liye swaryan baham pohanchai jayen, aur jab tum ne kaha ke mein tumahray liye swaryon ka intizam nahi karsaktha to woh majaburan wapas gay aur haal yeh tha ke un ki aankhon se ansoo jari thay aur inhen is baat ka bara ranj tha ke woh apne kharch par shareek jehaad honay ki mqdrt nahi rakhtay"
9,93,"Albata aitraaz un logon par hai jo maldaar hain aur phir bhi tum se darkhwasten karte hain ke inhen shirkat jehaad se maaf rakha jaye unhon ne ghar bethnay valyon mein shaamil hona pasand kya aur Allah ne un ke dilon par thp_h laga diya, is liye ab yeh kuch nahi jantay ( ke Allah ke haan un ki rawish ka kya nateeja niklny wala hai )"
